# Conservative ignores for faster fd/rg scans in $HOME
# Keep this minimal to avoid hiding useful project files.
AppData/
.cache/
.pnpm-store/
npm-cache/
**/node_modules/
**/.cache/**
**/cache/**
.cargo/
.lmstudio/
.vscode/
.dotnet/

# --- pi @mention noise reduction (home directory) ---

# Vendor/dependency spam
**/vendor/

# Tool/vendor content that floods README hits
.agents/skills/

# Optional: suppress README noise from hidden tool dirs
**/.*/**/README
**/.*/**/README.md

# Keep important local docs visible
!README.md
!.config/**/README.md
!.agent/**/README.md